The former senator representing Kaduna Central Senatorial District, Shehu Sani has taken to his verified Twitter page to say all the presidential aspirants of the All Progressive Party, APC have solutions to the problem of Nigeria.
As the 2023 presidential election is fast approaching, all the presidential aspirants have started airing out their respective packages on how to solve the country’s problem.
However, the governorship aspirant, Shehu Sani has reacted to this. According to Sani, he said all the presidential aspirants from the ruling party have magical packages of answers to the challenges Nigeria is currently facing.
Adding to this, Shehu asked that since all of them have this gift of wisdom to solve the problems of this country, then why did they deny their principal of it.
In his tweet, Shehu Sani wrote below:
“All the presidential aspirants of the ruling party have magical packages of solutions to the problems of this country. Why did they deny their principal this gift of wisdom?”



